  "why": "The paper designs and enforces metamorphic, semantics-preserving audio transformations and explicitly restricts repeated/distorting mutations across a mutant’s transformation history. It (1) constrains single-step transformation parameters to preserve human-recognizable semantics and (2) enforces a rule that prevents applying multiple volume/speed/clearness mutations to the same seed chain (thus preventing cumulative drift across iterations). The oracle also relies on metamorphic semantics (WER/CER threshold). These mechanisms enforce both semantic consistency and naturalness across fuzzing iterations.",
